event.title: Video Playback Seek Completed
event.description: Playback delivers seeked position of content or ad

properties.name: ad_enabled
properties.description: false if the user has any ad blockers

properties.name: content_asset_id
properties.description: Asset Id of the video playing/about to be played

properties.name: content_pod_id
properties.description: Pod Id of the video playing/about to be played

properties.name: full_screen
properties.description: true if playback is in full screen mode

properties.name: livestream
properties.description: True f the playback will be a livetream

properties.name: position
properties.description: Position of product in the list

properties.name: seek_position
properties.description: Playhead position in seconds where the user is seeking to

properties.name: session_id
properties.description: The unique ID of the overall session.

properties.name: sound
properties.description: The sound level of the playback

properties.name: total_length
properties.description: Total duration of the playback in seconds

properties.name: video_player
properties.description: The name of the video player (ie ‘youtube’, ‘vimeo’).
